title: 'Not as soft as expected'
body: 'Expected more soft tissues but it isnt'

title: 'single ply bad quality napkins'
body: 'The napkins are rough and not good absorbent. One napkin would not suffice a single requirement and thus end up using the entire pack a lot earlier than expected. Several other brands such as origami white knight provide good quality napkins in similar price range. i do not recommend these.'

title: 'Not 2 Ply Napkins'
body: 'Absolutely useless napkins. They are not 2 ply and are transparently thin making them of no use as far as absorbency is concerned. You will require several napkins together to wipe off any spilt liquid or wet hands.'

title: 'IT WAS ONE PLY'
body: As per production description, it was supposed to be 2 PLY.  But 4 packets of 1 ply tissue was delivered.  Don't mislead consumers.

title: 'Do read it'
body: I don't go around writing reviews but I thought this is very important , these napkins are sooo thin they dissolve after they get into the contact of air itself so it's not going to be of any use at all.. so don't even bother to buy them.. having them and not having them is like the same thing
